@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - Durban Girls Secondary School</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@700;800&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --navy-deep: #050c18;
            --navy-card: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.85);
            --navy-accent: #112240;
            --gold-accent: #c5a059;
            --white-bright: #e6f1ff;
            --white-muted: #8892b0;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
            background: var(--navy-deep);
            color: var(--white-muted);
            line-height: 1.8;
            /* Ensures scrollability even on high-res screens */
            min-height: 120vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .page-bg-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(5, 12, 24, 0.98), rgba(5, 12, 24, 0.85)), url('/Content/Images/tp-image-3986.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            background: rgba(5, 12, 24, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--navy-accent);
        }

        .nav-logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .school-crest-nav {
            height: 45px;
            filter: brightness(0.9);
        }

        .nav-logo-text {
            font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white-bright);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .nav-links-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .nav-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--white-muted);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .nav-link:hover, .active-link {
                color: var(--gold-accent);
            }

        .btn-portal {
            border: 1px solid var(--gold-accent);
            color: var(--gold-accent);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* Main Container - Left Aligned */
        .about-main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 160px 5% 100px;
            text-align: left; /* Removed centering */
        }

        .section-tag {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--gold-accent);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white-bright);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 0.9;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        /* Stats Grid */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 8rem; /* Increased spacing to force scroll */
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--navy-card);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: left; /* Left align stats content */
            border: 1px solid var(--navy-accent);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .stat-number {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--gold-accent);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white-muted);
        }

        /* Content Blocks - Scrolled & Left Aligned */
        .content-section {
            background: var(--navy-card);
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 4rem; /* Increased gap */
            border: 1px solid var(--navy-accent);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-accent);
            max-width: 900px; /* Keeps line length readable while left-aligned */
        }

            .content-section h2 {
                font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
                font-size: 2rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                color: var(--white-bright);
                letter-spacing: 1px;
            }

            .content-section p {
                font-size: 1.15rem;
                color: var(--white-muted);
                font-weight: 300;
            }

        /* CTA - Stays prominent */
        .cta-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--navy-accent), var(--navy-deep));
            padding: 6rem 4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 8rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold-accent);
            max-width: 1000px;
        }

            .cta-panel h3 {
                font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
                font-size: 3rem;
                color: var(--white-bright);
                text-transform: uppercase;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

        .btn-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
            background: var(--gold-accent);
            color: var(--navy-deep);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 5rem 5%;
            text-align: left;
            background: var(--navy-deep);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--navy-accent);
        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links-wrapper {
                display: none;
            }

            .content-section {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .about-main {
                padding-top: 120px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="page-bg-overlay"></div>

    <nav>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="nav-logo-container">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/za-368-kzn-dgss.jpg" alt="DGSS Crest" class="school-crest-nav" />
            <div class="nav-logo-text">DGSS<br>Secondary</div>
        </a>

        <ul class="nav-links-wrapper">
            <li><a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")" class="nav-link active-link">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>

        <a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Teachers")" class="btn-portal">Staff Portal</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="about-main">
        <span class="section-tag">Historical Legacy / Est. 1882</span>
        <h1>Institutional Profile & Strategic Vision</h1>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">144</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Years of Heritage</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">1200+</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Learner Population</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">Quintile 4</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Resource Managed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Pass Rate Benchmark</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Strategic Excellence</h2>
            <p>Durban Girls Secondary School operates at the intersection of academic rigor and socio-economic inclusivity. We maintain a highly structured management environment where excellence is not just encouraged but expected. Our robust systems ensure that world-class education remains accessible to all who exhibit the character to pursue it.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Campus Ecosystem</h2>
            <p>Our facility serves as a vital training ground for over 1,200 future leaders. By fostering a culture of professional discipline and critical inquiry, we prepare young women to navigate the complexities of a global economy. Every classroom is a node for character building, ethical leadership, and high-performance output.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Future-Ready Framework</h2>
            <p>The academic framework at DGSS is optimized for the 21st-century economy. With a heavy emphasis on STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics), Financial Literacy, and Social Sciences, we provide our learners with the intellectual infrastructure required to drive South Africa’s growth in an increasingly competitive landscape.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="cta-panel">
            <h3>Initiate Your Future</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--white-muted); font-size: 1.2rem;">Character. Competence. Community. <br>Join the legacy of Durban's leading secondary institution.</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Register", "Parents")" class="btn-cta">Start 2027 Application</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold-accent); margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;">Onward and Upward</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--white-muted);">&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year DURBAN GIRLS SECONDARY SCHOOL. <br>PROUDLY COMMITTED TO ACADEMIC INTEGRITY.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>